name: El Rey Conquista Eldlich
text:
1 "Eldlich" monster + 1 Level 5 or higher Zombie monster
This card's name becomes "Eldlich the Golden Lord" while in the Monster Zone. Cannot be destroyed by battle or card effects. You can Tribute 1 Zombie monster, then target 1 face-up monster your opponent controls; take control of it, also it cannot attack or activate its effects until the end of this turn. You can only use this effect of "El Rey Conquista Eldlich" once per turn.
